data.description: ADD. $5,000 TOWARDS BUYERS CLOSING COSTS & BUYER HAS ASSUMABLE MORTGAGE AT 3.75%. Don't miss this beautiful & spacious home on a large corner lot in Marine Creek Ranch! Downstairs features an open living, kitchen & dining areas with a private office at the front of the home. The kitchen boasts beautiful granite countertops, subway tile backsplash, white cabinets, & stainless steel appliances with a gas range. All four bedrooms are upstairs with a cozy game room or flex space area. The master suite offers additional room for seating with a large master bath & walk-in closet. The backyard has a storage shed, large covered patio, oversized side gate with room to park a trailer, boat, etc. HVAC has a 10 yr transferable warranty. Ideal location just minutes from shopping & restaurants with easy access to HWY 820. This neighborhood includes numerous amenities - clubhouse, pool, playground, picnic area, & dock. Walking & bike trails are located within walking distance at Marine Creek Lake!
